《'''我的希臘甜心'''》（原名：{{lang|fr|''Xenia''}}；[[希臘語|希臘語]]：{{lang|el|''Ξενία''}}）是一部[[2014年電影|2014年]]的[[劇情片|劇情片]]，由{{tsl|en|Panos H. Koutras|帕諾斯·庫特拉斯}}導演。影片入圍2014年[[坎城影展|坎城影展]]的「一種注目」單元<ref name="Cannes2014">{{cite web |url=http://www.festival-cannes.fr/en/article/60533.html |title=2014 Official Selection |accessdate=12 May 2014 |work=Cannes |archive-date=2015-12-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151202011024/http://www.festival-cannes.fr/en/article/60533.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>和[[多倫多國際影展|多倫多國際影展]]的「當代電影世界」單元，<ref name="TIFF">{{cite web |url=http://www.indiewire.com/article/toronto-international-film-festival-reveals-7-big-new-lineups-20140812 |title=TIFF Adds 'Clouds of Sils Maria' and 'Two Days, One Night,' Reveals 5 More Lineups |accessdate=28 August 2014 |work=Indiewire |archive-date=2015-12-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151228230753/http://www.indiewire.com/article/toronto-international-film-festival-reveals-7-big-new-lineups-20140812 |dead-url=no }}</ref>並代表希臘於[[第88屆奧斯卡金像獎|第88屆奧斯卡金像獎]]競選[[奧斯卡最佳外語片獎|奧斯卡最佳外語片獎]]，但未獲提名。<ref name="GreekReporter">{{cite web |url=http://hollywood.greekreporter.com/2015/09/04/xenia-greeces-submission-to-the-2016-academy-awards/ |title=‘Xenia': Greece’s Submission to the 2016 Academy Awards |work=Greek Reporter |date=4 September 2015 |accessdate=4 September 2015 |archive-date=2016-07-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160722115906/http://hollywood.greekreporter.com/2015/09/04/xenia-greeces-submission-to-the-2016-academy-awards/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="Greece">{{cite web |url=http://blogs.indiewire.com/thompsononhollywood/foreign-oscar-submissions-so-far-trailers-20150902 |title=Foreign Oscar Submissions So Far |last=Thompson |first=Anne |work=Indie Wire |date=3 September 2015 |accessdate=3 September 2015 |archive-date=2016-03-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160303234640/http://blogs.indiewire.com/thompsononhollywood/foreign-oscar-submissions-so-far-trailers-20150902 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

